OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1987FThe first edition of The Roxy
OL,7,Fairs on ITV. A new pop show, hosted by
OL,8,FDavid 'Kid' Jensen and Kevin Sharkey.
OL,9,FThe Tyne Tees TV-produced show was
OL,10,Fdropped after ten months.
OL,11,
OL,12,FTV Times: "At last! The Roxy, the venue
OL,13,Ffor ITV's new pop chart show, opens for
OL,14,Fbusiness. A galaxy of British and
OL,15,Finternational recording stars welcome
OL,16,Fthe arrival of the nation's glossiest
OL,17,Fand best showcase for up-to-the-minute
OL,18,Fmusic talent. Animation, videos, gossip
OL,19,Fand startling stage performances add up
OL,20,Fto a weekly event no pop fan should
OL,21,Fmiss."
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
