OL,6,CG1992FThe first edition of Summer
OL,7,FScene airs on BBC One.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG2001FThe Joy of Text - Live airs on
OL,10,FBBC One. Radio Times: "An evening
OL,11,Fdevoted to what is fast becoming the
OL,12,Fmost popular form of communication -
OL,13,Ftext messaging. Ulrika Jonsson and
OL,14,FTerry Alderton introduce interactive
OL,15,Ffun and games with the numbers to call
OL,16,Ffor viewers to text message their jokes
OL,17,Ffor publication."
